<span id="freeTextContainer17767368439984060916">I thoroughly enjoyed reading about Coretta&apos;s childhood, formal education, music career, and involvement in many movements during and after MLK&apos;s life. The stories told by her sister humanize the characters and bring color to a story I only knew the highlights of. <br/><br/>There is a lot of detail in the timelines that can read a little slow but overall enjoyable and most importantly the kind of book that makes you wiser for consuming it.</span>
  <span id="freeText17767368439984060916" style="display:none">I thoroughly enjoyed reading about Coretta's childhood, formal education, music career, and involvement in many movements during and after MLK's life. The stories told by her sister humanize the characters and bring color to a story I only knew the highlights of. <br /><br />There is a lot of detail in the timelines that can read a little slow but overall enjoyable and most importantly the kind of book that makes you wiser for consuming it.</span>
