<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11210574462967882774">Edythe Scott Bagley was an American author, activist, and educator. The older sister of Coretta Scott King, she worked behind the scenes to promote the Civil Rights Movement and was actively involved in many of the crucial events of that era.</span>

